data.meta_description:
11K likes, 81 comments - zebablay on December 6, 2022: "Moments of Black joy, love and tenderness 

(1. Toni Morrison celebrating her Nobel Prize in Literature win with friends  2. Danai Gurira meeting Sheryl Lee Ralph at the premiere of Wakanda Forever 3. A young ballerina and her teacher, image source unknown 4. @ recoveryandhealing on TikTok reacting to her best friend cleaning and organizing her room after traveling 5. Lauren London celebrating her 30th birthday in 2014 6. @ tekab0 on TikTok singing with her kids 7. Avis and Evie Pendavis at the House of Chanel Ball in 1990, shot by Chantal Regnault 8. @yesaurielle unboxing and trying on a red carpet dress Lizzo sent them to wear to the Out 100 gala 9. A couple shares a kiss, a rainbow in the distance, source unknown 10. @trapselyna on splitting the bill)".
